[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/comments/478433540","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2#issuecomment-478433540","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2","id":478433540,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQ3ODQzMzU0MA==","user":{"login":"luopeixiang","id":16150164,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTUwMTY0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16150164?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-04-01T04:42:49Z","updated_at":"2019-04-01T04:42:49Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"> 您好，我对数据集内容还有部分疑问，烦请解答\r\n> 1、项目中dev\\test\\train三个文件分别是做什么用的数据集？\r\n> 2、这些数据集中的标注是人工标注的吗？\r\n> 3、训练好的模型是如何测试准确率的？\r\n> 谢谢!\r\n\r\n1.项目中的数据集是2018 ACL论文[Chinese NER using Lattice LSTM](https://arxiv.org/abs/1805.02023)中收集的简历数据，这篇论文就是研究中文实体识别的，这些数据是论文作者从[新浪财经](http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/index.shtml)爬取的，用于证明论文中提出的lattice LSTM方法的有效性。原论文关于这个数据是这么写的：\r\n\r\n>For more variety in test domains, we collected a\r\n>resume dataset from Sina Finance, which consists\r\n>of resumes of senior executives from listed compa-\r\n>nies in the Chinese stock market. We randomly se-\r\n>lected 1027 resume summaries and manually an-\r\n>notated 8 types of named entities with YEDDA\r\n>system (Yang et al., 2018).\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n2.数据集是人工标注的。\r\n\r\n3.测试准确率是先计算模型预测的标注中有多少个标注是正确的，将这个数除以标注的总数即为准确率。假设我们的目标标注是\"B O O O E\"，而模型预测的标注是\"B O O B E\"，这个时候正确的标注有四个，总的标注数为5，那么准确率就是4/5 = 80%.\r\n\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/comments/478433540/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"luopeixiang","id":16150164,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTUwMTY0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16150164?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/comments/478435361","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2#issuecomment-478435361","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2","id":478435361,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQ3ODQzNTM2MQ==","user":{"login":"beagood","id":49052189,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ5MDUyMTg5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/