s","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/beagood/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/beagood/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/comments/478436448","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2#issuecomment-478436448","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2","id":478436448,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQ3ODQzNjQ0OA==","user":{"login":"luopeixiang","id":16150164,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTUwMTY0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16150164?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-04-01T05:02:00Z","updated_at":"2019-04-01T05:02:00Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"> 感谢您的回复，对于第一个问题我还有一点疑问。\r\n> dev\\test\\train三个文件分别是做什么的？\r\n> 我理解中，train数据集用来训练模型，之后用test数据集进行测试，但不知道dev数据集的作用。\r\n> 烦请再次解答，感谢！\r\n\r\ndev是验证集，是用来调节模型超参数的。在一些模型中，像SVM模型中的核函数，LSTM的层数、隐向量的维数就是模型的超参数，验证集是用来比较相同的模型下，哪种超参数效果比较好进而选择该超参数下的模型作为结果（比如在验证集上的测试结果表明，LSTM选择1层的效果要比2层效果好，那我们就将LSTM模型的层数设置为1层）\r\n如果还不明白，可以看看下面这些博客：\r\nhttps://blog.csdn.net/Neleuska/article/details/73193096\r\nhttps://blog.csdn.net/u014038273/article/details/80145317\r\nhttps://blog.csdn.net/JNingWei/article/details/78170171\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/comments/478436448/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"luopeixiang","id":16150164,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTUwMTY0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16150164?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/luopeixiang/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/comments/478436689","html_url":"https://github.com/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2#issuecomment-478436689","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/luopeixiang/named_entity_recognition/issues/2","id":478436689,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQ3ODQzNjY4OQ==","user":{"login":"beagood","id":49052189,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ5MDUyMTg5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/49052189?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/beagood","html_url":"https://github.com/beagood","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/beagood/followers","